data.description: Welcome to this beautiful Ranch in the Austintown School District! 3-4 Beds, 2 Baths, 2 attached Garage, corner Home. Main level Bonus Room has 150 Sq. Ft. Basement is partially finished. Upgrades include: Stainless steel Kitchen appliances (5 years old); Garbage Disposal (1 year old); front Porch built in 2022; front portion of the Roof was replaced in 2022. Call for a private showing before it's gone!
